- "Premium Deals" displays items with discounts exclusive for the Premium Members
- "Everyone is after these products" displays items with discounts based on total net worth of products from a specific merchant
- "Special discounts for popular categories" displays items with standalone discounts
- "Bestsellers in daily needs" popular by views/orders items from Groceries/Cosmetics/Hygiene categories
- "You can also check out these products" displays items from the same category as the viewed product
- "Recommended advertised products" displays products with active marketing campaign from the same category as the viewed product
- "Those who looked at this received" displays items bought by customers who had also viewed the currently viewed item
- "Products purchased by those who viewed this"
- "Everyone is looking at these" the most viewed items of the same category
- "taken together" displays items that are often checked out in the same cart with the viewed product
- "Most viewed products right now" displays items that are most often visited by the customers during the specific recent period
- "Current best sellers" displays most purchased items during the specific recent period